1. *Pejdž* je bio popularan uređaj tokom 90-ih godina. (*Pejdž* was a popular device during the 90s.)
2. Potrebno mi je da kupim novi *pejdž*. (I need to buy a new *pejdž*.)
3. Ovaj *pejdž* je već bio u kvaru kada sam ga kupio. (This *pejdž* was already broken when I bought it.)
4. Molim te, pozovi me kada vidiš *pejdž*. (Please call me when you see the *pejdž*.)
5. *Pejdž* je bio prvi mobilni uređaj koji sam imao. (*Pejdž* was the first mobile device I had.)
6. Šta misliš o zamenskoj bateriji za *pejdž*? (What do you think about the replacement battery for *pejdž*?)
7. Da li je ovaj *pejdž* još uvek aktivan? (Is this *pejdž* still active?)
8. Ne mogu da se setim gde sam ostavio svoj *pejdž*. (I can't remember where I left my *pejdž*.)
9. Pre nego što smo imali mobilne telefone, *pejdž* je bio najbolji način za komunikaciju na daljinu. (Before we had mobile phones, *pejdž* was the best way for long-distance communication.)
10. Kada sam prvi put dobio *pejdž*, bio sam oduševljen. (When I first got a *pejdž*, I was thrilled.)